      "note": "<5% ΔF/F for a 100-mV depolarizing step (-70 → +30 mV) in HEK293 cells under widefield (one-photon) voltage clamp, 75 W Xenon arc lamp with GFP filter set. Single representative trial (Fig. 2a). The larger ~10% signal at +130 mV (a 200-mV step) is partly pH-confounded by Hv channel activation and is not used as the 100-mV dynamic range; an averaged value of ~8% ΔF/F for the 200-mV step is reported in Fig. 2b.",
